{% comment %}
  Gharyaal Hamburger Menu - Configuration-Based Navigation
  
  TO EDIT THE MENU: Scroll down to the menu_items section below and edit the list
  
  FORMAT:
  - parent|handle|Name - Creates a collection link (with or without dropdown)
  - sub|handle|Name - Creates a subcategory under the last parent
  - link|url|Name - Creates a custom link
  
  IMPORTANT: 
  - One item per line
  - Order matters - items appear in the order you list them
  - Subcategories must come AFTER their parent
{% endcomment %}

